Full Release

** Install from package manager

Use the package for your distro to install the package

Packages available for:
1) Ubuntu
2) Debian
3) Gentoo
4) Arch

** Install using included scripts
You can use the install/uninstall scripts to install/uninstall the program on every distro

	INSTALL:

Untar the tarball and run as root the install.sh script 

	UNINSTALL:

On the folder where you untar the program run the uninstall.sh script 

Please delete on your own the folder ~/.pysmssend 
